{"data":{"label":"Admonitions","index":3},"content":"<h1 id=\"admonitions\">Admonitions</h1><p>To create an admonition, simply use a special syntax that starts with <code>!!!</code> followed by the type of admonition you want, such as <code>note</code>, <code>warning</code>, <code>info</code>, etc., and the title of the admonition.</p>\n<p>For example, to create a note admonition, use <code>!!! note Your Note Title</code> and then add your note content.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs\">!!! info Admonition title\nAdmonition content\n!!!</code></pre><div class=\"admonition admonition-info\">\n    <p class=\"admonition-title\">Admonition title</p>\n    <p>Admonition content</p>\n\n    </div><p>The different admonition types are: <code>abstract</code>, <code>attention</code>, <code>bug</code>, <code>caution</code>, <code>danger</code>, <code>error</code>, <code>example</code>, <code>failure</code>, <code>hint</code>, <code>info</code>, <code>note</code>, <code>question</code>, <code>quote</code>, <code>success</code>, <code>tip</code>, <code>warning</code>.</p>\n<h1 id=\"examples\">Examples</h1><h2 id=\"grey\">Grey</h2><div class=\"admonition admonition-note\">\n    <p class=\"admonition-title\">demo for <strong>note</strong></p>\n    <p>content for <strong>note</strong></p>\n\n    </div><div class=\"admonition admonition-quote\">\n    <p class=\"admonition-title\">demo for <strong>quote</strong></p>\n    <p>content for <strong>quote</strong></p>\n\n    </div><h2 id=\"blue\">Blue</h2><div class=\"admonition admonition-abstract\">\n    <p class=\"admonition-title\">demo for <strong>abstract</strong></p>\n    <p>content for <strong>abstract</strong></p>\n\n    </div><div class=\"admonition admonition-info\">\n    <p class=\"admonition-title\">demo for <strong>info</strong></p>\n    <p>content for <strong>info</strong></p>\n\n    </div><div class=\"admonition admonition-question\">\n    <p class=\"admonition-title\">demo for <strong>question</strong></p>\n    <p>content for <strong>question</strong></p>\n\n    </div><h2 id=\"green\">Green</h2><div class=\"admonition admonition-hint\">\n    <p class=\"admonition-title\">demo for <strong>hint</strong></p>\n    <p>content for <strong>hint</strong></p>\n\n    </div><div class=\"admonition admonition-success\">\n    <p class=\"admonition-title\">demo for <strong>success</strong></p>\n    <p>content for <strong>success</strong></p>\n\n    </div><div class=\"admonition admonition-tip\">\n    <p class=\"admonition-title\">demo for <strong>tip</strong></p>\n    <p>content for <strong>tip</strong></p>\n\n    </div><h2 id=\"orange\">Orange</h2><div class=\"admonition admonition-bug\">\n    <p class=\"admonition-title\">demo for <strong>bug</strong></p>\n    <p>content for <strong>bug</strong></p>\n\n    </div><div class=\"admonition admonition-caution\">\n    <p class=\"admonition-title\">demo for <strong>caution</strong></p>\n    <p>content for <strong>caution</strong></p>\n\n    </div><div class=\"admonition admonition-warning\">\n    <p class=\"admonition-title\">demo for <strong>warning</strong></p>\n    <p>content for <strong>warning</strong></p>\n\n    </div><h2 id=\"red\">Red</h2><div class=\"admonition admonition-attention\">\n    <p class=\"admonition-title\">demo for <strong>attention</strong></p>\n    <p>content for <strong>attention</strong></p>\n\n    </div><div class=\"admonition admonition-danger\">\n    <p class=\"admonition-title\">demo for <strong>danger</strong></p>\n    <p>content for <strong>danger</strong></p>\n\n    </div><div class=\"admonition admonition-error\">\n    <p class=\"admonition-title\">demo for <strong>error</strong></p>\n    <p>content for <strong>error</strong></p>\n\n    </div><div class=\"admonition admonition-failure\">\n    <p class=\"admonition-title\">demo for <strong>failure</strong></p>\n    <p>content for <strong>failure</strong></p>\n\n    </div><h2 id=\"others\">Others</h2><div class=\"admonition admonition-example\">\n    <p class=\"admonition-title\">demo for <strong>example</strong></p>\n    <p>content for <strong>example</strong></p>\n\n    </div>","label":"Admonitions"}